sg":"英文唔係得一種表達方式 你驚d grammar表達錯咪加d字眼令人更明白個時間點"},{"pid":"46629123cdc5b7f3484dd7fc7e697997cebecba7","tid":1029271,"uid":101507,"like":6,"dislike":4,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-20T06:37:56.000Z","msg":"個said字係past tense，已經表達左佢講依句野既時間係發生喺過去<br />\n至於用hates定hated就在於條友依家仲憎唔憎佢老豆，仲憎就hates，唔憎就hated<br />\n<br />\n唔知有冇錯，希望解答到你既問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"768dc9314c8aedd1ea1407365b3b4b730ec81d2a","tid":1029271,"uid":32782,"like":2,"dislike":10,"score":-8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-20T06:44:17.000Z","msg":"我理解係因為你陳述人地嘅事 而嗰件事已經假設過左去先要轉過去式<br />\n<br />\n但係你陳述緊人地件事嗰陣 件事依然發生緊就唔洗轉<br />\n<br />\n最簡單 我老母同我講太陽由東邊出來<br />\nMy mum told me that the sun is always raising from the east."},{"pid":"0fb68ef5cbc4009a56c07c48bce55f6a5090ffbc","tid":1029271,"uid":130105,"like":1,"dislike":16,"score":-15,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-20T06:44:46.000Z","msg":"樓主唔好話白痴，這個問題我都因『妖』好耐。<br />\n<br />\nhe says that he hates his father"},{"pid":"b7f8d449c82302681103750e3bae43275aa17645","tid":1029271,"uid":196266,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-20T06:45:11.000Z","msg":"Still true的話，「可以」唔轉過去式。因為係reported speech裡面，用過去式唔代表時間上真係過去。所以過去式同現在式都係能夠接受<br />\n<br />\n但係仍然憎嘅情況下用hated，人地可能有疑問，如果想避免呢個情況，一係就用現在式，一係就補充多啲資訊。但係文法上黎講，兩者都被接受"},{"pid":"1e5090fdc7ff5c2e9293c08588eb5adbdbf29d17","tid":1029271,"uid":47954,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-20T06:50:59.000Z","msg":"He killed his father"},{"pid":"e7d1a01f80451b5b7bf5a300ade996a3dd85e0a1","tid":1029271,"uid":48222,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0fb68ef5cbc4009a56c07c48bce55f6a5090ffbc","tid":1029271,"uid":130105,"like":1,"dislike":16,"score":-15,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-20T06:44:46.000Z","msg":"樓主唔好話白痴，這個問題我都因『妖』好耐。<br />\n<br />\nhe says that he hates his father"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-20T07:14:03.000Z","msg":"困擾？"},{"pid":"a4cd287dd72f15aa668214a4f90b71eae8ff6adf","tid":1029271,"uid":112551,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-20T07:22:18.000Z","msg":"he said that his father is being hated by him"},{"pid":"9d2d00d68f9afcbc2e81e9545696a433f8db1bd1","tid":1029271,"uid":7123,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-20T07:22:36.000Z","msg":"兩種情況<br />\n現在唔確定有否繼續發生 現在式就轉過去式 總之相對轉過去一級<br />\n現在仍存在，事實 不用轉變"},{"pid":"77b3899ec9ab469a3a6597e097873c65b51d6926","tid":1029271,"uid":31029,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-20T07:23:18.000Z","msg":"上連登問英文<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7fe1a61ccc4424459e879012a57a3619333f0b31","tid":1029271,"uid":69125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-20T07:27:14.000Z","msg":"佢講嘅時候係憎,依家唔知/唔憎:hated<br />\n其他:hates"},{"pid":"4b0cd82156a42e659c4bf1ee53b56141e48a5687","tid":1029271,"uid":175990,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-20T07:29:14.000Z","msg":"<strong>Hated 啊 傻仔</strong>"},{"pid":"93ee62dd18240ac1579905a5b3c5224e96168eba","tid":1029271,"uid":203256,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"768dc9314c8aedd1ea1407365b3b4b730ec81d2a","tid":1029271,"uid":32782,"like":2,"dislike":10,"score":-8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-20T06:44:17.000Z","msg":"我理解係因為你陳述人地嘅事 而嗰件事已經假設過左去先要轉過去式<br />\n<br />\n但係你陳述緊人地件事嗰陣 件事依然發生緊就唔洗轉<br />\n<br />\n最簡單 我老母同我講太陽由東邊出來<br />\nMy mum told me that the sun is always raising from the east."},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-20T07:34:26.000Z","msg":"raising<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d77fcbce12d0cbea33c9f766065accbdef4bb31","tid":1029271,"uid":75537,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"a606134ce436effb7d7f0a2d4f0ecc831b998921","tid":1029271,"uid":50658,"like":432,"dislike":4,"score":428,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-20T06:25:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>想問下例如要寫report 要寫返有個人話&ldquo;我好憎老豆&rdquo;<br />\n咁應該係用<span style=\"color: red;\">he said that he hates his father</span><br />\n定係<span style=\"color: red;\">he said that he hates his father</span>?<br />\n<br />\n因為我想表達我認為佢依家都仲係憎老豆</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n玩緊找不同?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-20T07:37:44.000Z","msg":"個分別就係有無問號"},{"pid":"62b3e9fa85efe2b00dd810d41a29d65c49685435","tid":1029271,"uid":176802,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"0fb68ef5cbc4009a56c07c48bce55f6a5090ffbc","tid":1029271,"uid":130105,"like":1,"dislike":16,"score":-15,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-20T06:44:46.000Z","msg":"樓主唔好話白痴，這個問題我都因『妖』好耐。<br />\n<br />\nhe says that he hates his father"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-20T07:39:16.000Z","msg":"乜撚野因妖"},{"pid":"0f83bc503e7e768658e7a8da6759298bf9c59487","tid":1029271,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-20T07:40:37.000Z","msg":"is hating"},{"pid":"9b3da3190fc34d2a62ec7e9734876e3eb5ac9f5e","tid":1029271,"uid":236401,"like":7,"dislike":4,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-20T07:44:36.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d0cf82bb8ed170ba33eb24d0a1a3ff4516976f49","tid":1029271,"uid":236401,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-20T07:45:16.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"13b44d7bce9728aa464d473b6319822fd619fa33","tid":1029271,"uid":20924,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"9b3da3190fc34d2a62ec7e9734876e3eb5ac9f5e","tid":1029271,"uid":236401,"like":7,"dislike":4,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"3ba04883372ff22432499e2d7686c40b628ae30d","tid":1029271,"uid":217679,"like":40,"dislike":31,"score":9,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-20T06:27:55.000Z","msg":"應該係Hate 呀<br />\nHated 係比人曾經憎恨，而家冇再憎既意思"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-20T07:44:36.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-20T07:50:35.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.perfect-english-grammar.com/reported-speech.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.perfect-english-grammar.com%2Freported-speech.html&d=WIvcVJ42Qixy%2BOT8%2FM1n87vH1KbbL%2ByyGPsbuV3zdoQ%3D&h=7049f6db\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.perfect-english-grammar.com/reported-speech.html</a><br />\n<br />\nOccasionally, we don't need to change the present tense into the past if the information in direct speech is still true"},{"pid":"fefcf526f719ad9ab37191f48349dbad68cf285c","tid":1029271,"uid":236401,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-20T07:51:10.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"db5d291ffb8b5f57ed6a97b36c5aea881df16b19","tid":1029271,"uid":236401,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-20T07:51:44.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7b918d7672941f376f6b268e62f3af0ca4363462","tid":1029271,"uid":37396,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"201331dd44885d6210bfec74e6f6227e712a15de","tid":1029271,"uid":92230,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-20T06:31:53.000Z","msg":"google reported speech 第一個結果已經解釋得幾清楚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://learnenglish.britishcouncil.org/intermediate-grammar/reported-speech-1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Flearnenglish.britishcouncil.org%2Fintermediate-grammar%2Freported-speech-1&d=WIvcVJ42Qixy%2BOT8%2FM1n87vH1KbbL%2ByyGPsbuV3zdoQ%3D&h=9b2e69c2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://learnenglish.britishcouncil.org/intermediate-grammar/reported-speech-1</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-20T07:51:52.000Z","msg":"樓主睇呢條link 啦<br />\n唔洗理連登啲on9 仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"76fe4c58a146888c9e389541fba3bc7a28170ae9","tid":1029271,"uid":20924,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"fefcf526f719ad9ab37191f48349dbad68cf285c","tid":1029271,"uid":236401,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"13b44d7bce9728aa464d473b6319822fd619fa33","tid":1029271,"uid":20924,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"9b3da3190fc34d2a62ec7e9734876e3eb5ac9f5e","tid":1029271,"uid":236401,"like":7,"dislike":4,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-20T07:44:36.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-20T07:50:35.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.perfect-english-grammar.com/reported-speech.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.perfect-english-grammar.com%2Freported-speech.html&d=WIvcVJ42Qixy%2BOT8%2FM1n87vH1KbbL%2ByyGPsbuV3zdoQ%3D&h=7049f6db\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.perfect-english-grammar.com/reported-speech.html</a><br />\n<br />\nOccasionally, we don't need to change the present tense into the past if the information in direct speech is still true"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-20T07:51:10.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-20T07:54:29.000Z","msg":"既然係咁 咁你憑咩咁權威教人tense要一致?<br />\n<br />\n你呢番言論等於：<br />\n「天鵝係白色架」<br />\n「下 邊度邊度有黑天鵝喎」<br />\n「屌 特別例子啫 總之天鵝係白色就無錯架喇」"},{"pid":"25b4543916b2e7d29dcbf45ef38d3dd27b9c7c2c","tid":1029271,"uid":176802,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-20T07:58:07.000Z","msg":"咁多傻鳩唔知咩係reported speech<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />仲喺到講乜鳩過去咗同未過去嘅分別"},{"pid":"f34b6ad41cad5ccb250b86dd50b78015f84e9e3a","tid":1029271,"uid":20924,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"25b4543916b2e7d29dcbf45ef38d3dd27b9c7c2c","tid":1029271,"uid":176802,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-20T07:58:07.000Z","msg":"咁多傻鳩唔知咩係reported speech<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />仲喺到講乜鳩過去咗同未過去嘅分別"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-20T08:05:48.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www.bbc.co.uk/worldservice/learningenglish/youmeus/learnit/learnitv71.shtml\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fworldservice%2Flearningenglish%2Fyoumeus%2Flearnit%2Flearnitv71.shtml&d=WIvcVJ42Qixy%2BOT8%2FM1n87vH1KbbL%2ByyGPsbuV3zdoQ%3D&h=d2e3d6ef\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.bbc.co.uk/worldservice/learningenglish/youmeus/learnit/learnitv71.shtml</a><br />\n<br />\nIf we are reporting a fact or something that is still true, the direct speech form can often be retained. So in your example, Richard, if the person you are talking about is still teaching then both these sentences are correct.<br />\n<br />\n&lsquo;She told me she was a teacher.&rsquo;<br />\n&lsquo;She told me she is a teacher.&rsquo;"},{"pid":"79bf32dd6f1f3e3bb86b3e3a3a89cabeb64820e3","tid":1029271,"uid":217679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9b3da3190fc34d2a62ec7e9734876e3eb5ac9f5e","tid":1029271,"uid":236401,"like":7,"dislike":4,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"3ba04883372ff22432499e2d7686c40b628ae30d","tid":1029271,"uid":217679,"like":40,"dislike":31,"score":9,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-20T06:27:55.000Z","msg":"應該係Hate 呀<br />\nHated 係比人曾經憎恨，而家冇再憎既意思"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-20T07:44:36.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-02-20T08:05:49.000Z","msg":"咁如果唔用hated, 應該點樣去表達佢曾經嬲過，而家冇再嬲呢<br />\n真心問<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1fd409e4d84a18fe47b271d051d161b80cb70d24","tid":1029271,"uid":236401,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-20T08:08:11.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"92a73b0220fc4191d607af3723ae9e90492631f3","tid":1029271,"uid":217679,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"79bf32dd6f1f3e3bb86b3e3a3a89cabeb64820e3","tid":1029271,"uid":217679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9b3da3190fc34d2a62ec7e9734876e3eb5ac9f5e","tid":1029271,"uid":236401,"like":7,"dislike":4,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"3ba04883372ff22432499e2d7686c40b628ae30d","tid":1029271,"uid":217679,"like":40,"dislike":31,"score":9,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-20T06:27:55.000Z","msg":"應該係Hate 呀<br />\nHated 係比人曾經憎恨，而家冇再憎既意思"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-20T07:44:36.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-02-20T08: