e had hated his father.<br />\n複述句裡面 Past tense=&gt;past perfect tense <br />\n<br />\n如果係佢話佢依家好嬲佢老豆，咁原句係<br />\nXXX: I hate my father.<br />\n<br />\nReported speech: He said he hated his father.<br />\nPresent tense=&gt;past tense <br />\n<br />\n另外有種程況係講fact<br />\ne.g. XXX: Hong Kong is an international city.<br />\n<br />\nReported speech: He said Hong Kong is an international city.<br />\n呢種係強調香港係國際城市係一個事實<br />\n<br />\nHe said Hong Kong was an international city.<br />\n呢種只係純粹想複述佢講左d咩<br />\n<br />\n2句都岩文法"},{"pid":"9f05881a5b7baf2b395a6b79bea630bb8f71fe4e","tid":1029271,"uid":35315,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-20T10:38:29.000Z","msg":"Hate(s)：依家憎<br />\nHated：曾經憎"},{"pid":"338f08c4f14286178b862cb7cf9aa54ee7ba8385","tid":1029271,"uid":35315,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"30cba87453c192e8b61385b55f6011c33c568ce1","tid":1029271,"uid":128761,"like":1,"dislike":13,"score":-12,"quote":{"pid":"4b2c951dd3f06fea1da7a67e0c9207e35c8ffcff","tid":1029271,"uid":160536,"like":83,"dislike":2,"score":81,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-20T06:25:25.000Z","msg":"He said that he hated his father"},"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-02-20T06:28:14.000Z","msg":"咁點樣強調佢依家都係憎老豆？<br />\n又或者再簡單d <br />\n佢話佢係女人<br />\n<br />\n咁應該係she said that she is a woman<br />\n定係she said that she was a woman?<br />\n<br />\n我知好白痴<br />\n但好似用現在又唔係用過去又唔係咁"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-20T10:39:41.000Z","msg":"is啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你用was一睇落去都會覺得奇怪啦<br />\n咩嘢佢話佢以前係女人，除非佢係變性人啦"},{"pid":"58ae8f27b9a10744ae387d853eddf13bab854468","tid":1029271,"uid":50028,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"4b2c951dd3f06fea1da7a67e0c9207e35c8ffcff","tid":1029271,"uid":160536,"like":83,"dislike":2,"score":81,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-20T06:25:25.000Z","msg":"He said that he hated his father"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-20T10:49:06.000Z","msg":"點解呢個comment 會咁多正評<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/c